<h1 class="text-success mb-3">About Jasper Green</h1>

<p>
    Jasper Green was founded by Jasper Jones, who started mowing neighborhood lawns
    in College Station as a teenager with a single push mower and strong work ethic.
</p>

<p>
    What began as a small side business has grown into a dependable lawn care company
    serving about 250 regular customers with a team of 21 employees.
</p>

<p>
    Today, Jasper Green operates 7 crews and provides mowing services across
    College Station and Bryan, Texas.
</p>
